title: Custom Designed Luxury Apartment
map_address: 19 Circle Dr. E near Cayford Dr.
posting_body: ['19 Circle Drive, Tiburon, CA', 'Whether you desire the cool morning breeze through the French doors that open up to your patio or the warmth of a fireplace clad in the finest Creama Marafil Marble, we have the home for you.', 'Our designer put careful thought into custom features such as cedar-lined closets with built-in closet organization systems.', 'The gourmet kitchen boasts a stainless steel appliance package, including an 50-bottle wine refrigerator with digital touch screen controls and temperature display.', 'Granite countertops, custom backsplash, and walnut cabinetry are the perfect blend of functionality and elegance.', 'You must see this custom home to understand the value of exquisite finishes carved out of a traditional apartment floor plan.', 'Relish in the thought of leasing a custom home without the pressure of a hefty down payment, a mortgage, and the added premium of land maintenance you don’t need.', 'Lease Terms', 'Deposit: $1500', 'Lease duration: 12 months', 'Details', '2 Beds / 2 Baths', 'Rent:', '$3,795', '/month', '950 square feet', 'Pets Allowed: Cats & Dogs', 'Amenities', 'Assigned Parking', 'Fireplace', 'In Unit Laundry']
